snippet.title: Match Highlights - Portugal 6:1 Switzerland - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
No Cristiano Ronaldo, no problem as Portugal crushed Switzerland 6-1 to reach the #FIFAWorldCup quarter-finals for the first time since 2006.

Goncalo Ramos was the star performer in #PORSUI as he netted a sensational hat-trick; the first of #Qatar2022. Pepe & Raphael Guerreiro also got their names on the scoresheet in between the Benfica striker's goals. Substitute Rafael Leao added the cherry on top of the icing with a sublime finish in injury time.

Manuel Akanji bagged the consolation for Switzerland.

Enjoy the highlights of this clash & remember to watch Portugal in action again on Dec 10 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

snippet.title: The Search For Coconuts Begins | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Watch the best moment from your beloved show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah where are characters are here to take you on a joyous ride. Get on the happy train and enjoy how these characters navigate through their daily lives in a hilarious way! Jethalal, Taarak, and all of the members eagerly await you.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1393
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #SonyPAL

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0GGKekdfESeKWx2JOF9NFL

snippet.title: श्री कृष्ण लीला | श्री कृष्ण ने अश्वत्थामा को दिया था श्राप
snippet.description:
भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

Watch the story of "Shree krshn ne ashvatthaama ko diya tha shraap" now!

Watch Janmashtami Special Krishna Bhajan - Govind Madhav Jai Jai Gopal by Dev Negi - http://bit.ly/GovindMadhavJaiJaiGopal

अश्वत्थामा ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को पांडवों पर छोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण अर्जुन को कहते हैं की तुम भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र का प्रयोग कर अश्वत्थामा के अस्त्र को रोकने के लिए कहते हैं। अर्जुन भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को चला देता है। वेदव्यास जी दोनों अस्त्रों के बीच में आकर उन्हें आपस में टकराने से रोक देते हैं और दोनों को अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेने के लिए कहते हैं अर्जुन उनकी बात मान कर अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेता है। लेकिन जब अश्वत्थामा उन्हें कहता है की मैं इस अस्त्र को वापस लेने की विद्या नहीं जानता। वेदव्यास जी अश्वत्थामा को कहते हैं की तुम इसे यदि वापस नहीं ले सकते तो तुम इसे पृथ्वी के उस हिस्से पर मोड़ दो जहां कोई भी जीव नहीं है और इसके बदले में तुम्हें पांडवों से अभय दान दिलवाता हूँ। श्री कृष्ण पांडवों से अश्वत्थामा को अभ्यदान देने के बदले उसकी दिव्य मणि को माँगते हैं जो की उसे सिर के भीतर थी जिस से उसे ना कभी भूक लगती थी और वह राज मुक्त रहता था। अश्वत्थामा अपने ब्रह्मषिर अभिमनयु की पत्नी उत्तरा के गर्भ की ओर मोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण उत्तरा के गर्भ की रक्षा करने के लिए अपने सुदर्शन चक्र को भेजते हैं। श्री कृष्ण ब्रह्मा जी से कहते हैं की आप अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लें क्योंकि अश्वत्थामा ने इसका प्रयोग ग़लत कार्य के लिए किया है। ब्रह्मा जी अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लेते हैं। श्री कृष्ण अश्वत्थामा को अपने कर्म के कारण श्राप देते हैं की तुम हज़ारों वर्षों के लिए इसी कल में जीवित रहोगे तुम्हें मृत्युु नहीं आएगी और तुमसे कोई भी इंसान बात नहीं करेगा और तुम्हारा शरीर ऐसा हो जाएगा की तुम स्वयं अपनी शक्ल को देख कर भी डर जाओगे। श्री कृष्ण भीम को अश्वत्थामा की दिव्य मणि निकल कर लाने के लिए कहते हैं। भीम उस मणि को उसके सर से निकल लेता है।

श्री कृष्ण के सभी एपिसोड और भजन देखने के लिए Subscribe करें तिलक YouTube चैनल को। 

Subscribe to Tilak for more devotional contents - https://bit.ly/SubscribeTilak

श्रीकृष्णा, रामानंद सागर द्वारा निर्देशित एक भारतीय टेलीविजन धारावाहिक है। मूल रूप से इस श्रृंखला का दूरदर्शन पर साप्ताहिक प्रसारण किया जाता था। यह धारावाहिक कृष्ण के जीवन से सम्बंधित कहानियों पर आधारित है। गर्ग संहिता , पद्म पुराण , ब्रह्मवैवर्त पुराण अग्नि पुराण, हरिवंश पुराण , महाभारत , भागवत पुराण , भगवद्गीता आदि पर बना धारावाहिक है सीरियल की पटकथा, स्क्रिप्ट एवं काव्य में बड़ौदा के महाराजा सयाजीराव विश्वविद्यालय के हिन्दी विभाग के अध्यक्ष डॉ विष्णु विराट जी ने महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका निभाई। इसे सर्वप्रथम दूरदर्शन के मेट्रो चैनल पर प्रसारित 1993 को किया गया था जो 1996 तक चला, 221 एपिसोड का यह धारावाहिक बाद में दूरदर्शन के डीडी नेशनल पर टेलीकास्ट हुआ, रामायण व महाभारत के बाद इसने टी आर पी के मामले में इसने दोनों धारावाहिकों को पीछे छोड़ दिया था,इसका पुनः जनता की मांग पर प्रसारण कोरोना महामारी 2020 में लॉकडाउन के दौरान रामायण श्रृंखला समाप्त होने के बाद ०३ मई से डीडी नेशनल पर किया जा रहा है, TRP के मामले में २१ वें हफ्ते तक यह सीरियल नम्बर १ पर कायम रहा। 

Produced - Ramanand Sagar / Subhash Sagar / Pren Sagar
Directed - Ramanand Sagar /  Aanand Sagar / Moti Sagar
Chief Asst. Director - Yogee Yogindar
Asst. Directors - Rajendra Shukla / Sridhar Jetty / Jyoti Sagar
Screenplay & Dialogues - Ramanand Sagar
Camera - Avinash Satoskar
Music - Ravindra Jain
Lyrics - Ravindra Jain 
Playback Singers - Suresh Wadkar / Hemlata / Ravindra Jain / Arvinder Singh / Sushil
Editor - Girish Daada / Moreshwar / R. Mishra / Sahdev

श्रीकृष्णा, रामानंद सागर द्वारा निर्देशित एक भारतीय टेलीविजन धारावाहिक है। मूल रूप से इस श्रृंखला का दूरदर्शन पर साप्ताहिक प्रसारण किया जाता था। यह धारावाहिक कृष्ण के जीवन से सम्बंधित कहानियों पर आधारित है। गर्ग संहिता , पद्म पुराण , ब्रह्मवैवर्त पुराण अग्नि पुराण, हरिवंश पुराण , महाभारत , भागवत पुराण , भगवद्गीता आदि पर बना धारावाहिक है सीरियल की पटकथा, स्क्रिप्ट एवं काव्य में बड़ौदा के महाराजा सयाजीराव विश्वविद्यालय के हिन्दी विभाग के अध्यक्ष डॉ विष्णु विराट जी ने महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका निभाई। इसे सर्वप्रथम दूरदर्शन के मेट्रो चैनल पर प्रसारित 1993 को किया गया था जो 1996 तक चला, 221 एपिसोड का यह धारावाहिक बाद में दूरदर्शन के डीडी नेशनल पर टेलीकास्ट हुआ, रामायण व महाभारत के बाद इसने टी आर पी के मामले में इसने दोनों धारावाहिकों को पीछे छोड़ दिया था,इसका पुनः जनता की मांग पर प्रसारण कोरोना महामारी 2020 में लॉकडाउन के दौरान रामायण श्रृंखला समाप्त होने के बाद ०३ मई से डीडी नेशनल पर किया जा रहा है, TRP के मामले में २१ वें हफ्ते तक यह सीरियल नम्बर १ पर कायम रहा।

snippet.title: Ghalib Hona Hai | Sukoon | Sanjay Leela Bhansali | Armaan Malik | Sharmin Segal | A. M. Turaz
snippet.description:
Find peace, quiet and love in the tunes of #SanjayLeelaBhansali's first-ever original music album #Sukoon!

Buy Carvaan Mobile- Feature phone with 1500 Pre-loaded songs at http://sarega.ma/ycmbuy

Credits:

Singer: Armaan Malik
Lyricist: A.M. Turaz
Music Director: Sanjay Leela Bhansali
Music Arranged and Programmed by: Shreyas Puranik & Rutvik Talashilkar 
Strokes: Tapas Roy
Tabla: Sanjeev Sen 
Rhythm & Percussions: Dipesh Varma 
Flute: Varad Kathapurkar
Guitars: Shomu Seal & Rutvik
Bass: Manas Chowdhary

Recording Studio:
Wow & Flutter (Tanay Gajjar) 
Ajivasan Sounds (Avdhoot Wadkar)

Mixing & Mastering @ Studio5o4 Engineer: Rahul M Sharma 
Assistant: Samir Dharap,Rohit Patil 
Atmos Mix @ Unifi Media Studio
Engineer: Nageshwar Rao Choudary, Rahul M Sharma 
Assistant: Deepak Poojari

Video Credits:

Featuring : Armaan Malik, Sharmin Segal

Video Directed By: Mitakshara Kumar 
DOP: Mahesh Limaye
Choreography: Kruti Mahesh  
Executive Producer : Arvinder Shagmer Gill
Chief Ad: Amit Tyagi
Director Assistants : Simran Segal, Rahul Sharma
 
Editor : Vineet Sharma 
Di Colorist: Ashirwad Hadkar 
Vfx Supervisors : Subroto Jalui, Shailesh Gautam (Famulus Media)
Production Design : Sandeep Ravade
Line Producer : Vikram A Yadav
Production Team: Kiran Gangurde,vishal Manohar

Team Sharmin Segal:
Manager: Kimberley Fernandes 
Makeup: Dipak Nayak
Hair Styling: Madhav Trehan
Stylists : Pranav Sood & Krisna Krishnankutty
Boy: Rohit Mer

Team Armaan:
Hair: Pratik Gaikwad
Makeup: Sushil Kumar Swami
Stylists : Pranav Sood & Krisna Krishnankutty

Lyrics:

Mukhda
Ishq Teri Ankhon Mein Likha
Padhne De Zara
Hum Ko Bhi Ghalib Hona Hai
In Ghazlon Si Ankhon Mein Khona Hai

1st Antara
Ghazlen Hum Tujh Pe Likhte Rahen
Shayar Ban Ban Ke Ugte Rahen.
Tera Chehera Koi Kitab Sa Hai
Tera Milna Koi Khwab Sa Hai
Iss Khwab Mein Khud Ko Dubona Hai

2nd Antara
Tere Hothon Se Sher Barasten Hain
Hum Baton Ko Teri Taraste Hain
Tera Hum Se Kalam Jo Ho Jaye
To Hamara Naam Bhi Ho Jaye
Teri Palkon Mein Khud Ko Perona Hai

snippet.title: GHANI SYAANI - MC SQUARE & Shehnaaz Gill | Rajat Nagpal | Anshul Garg | Latest Song
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Ghani Syaani by MC Square & Shehnaaz Gill. This is our first Haryanvi song. Tell us how do you like it in our comment section. 

Listen to full song here - 
https://INgrooves.lnk.to/GhaniSyaani

Singer: MC Square & Shehnaaz Gill
Lyricist: MC Square
Music: Rajat Nagpal
Guitars Rhythm Shaw
Sarangi Dilshad Khan
Mixed by Rajat Nagpal
Mastered by Naweed @Whitfield Mastering London
Recorded at Neo Sound , Mumbai

Featuring: MC Square & Shehnaaz Gill 

Producer: Anshul Garg

Director: Agam Mann & Azeem Mann
Project Head: Raghav Sharma 
Project Manager: Piyush Chandak, Gaurav Arora & Gaurav Bharti
DOP: Shinda Singh
Line Production: RS Films & Production 
Production Assistants: Honey, Rohit, Amir, Bablu 
Assistant Director: Rajat Yadav 
Creative Dir: John 
Local Production (Rajasthan: AM Films Production 
Art/Production Design:  Rajan Arts 
Steadicam Operator: Bijesh Chauhan 
Jimmy Jib Operator: Gaurav
Stills & BTS: Akki 
Costume Stylist: Outro by Akshita & Anulika
DI Colorist: Onkar Singh
Editing: Agam Mann 
Choreographer: Jayshree Dinesh Dhawan
Shehnaaz team :-
Business Manage: Kaushal Joshi 
Makeup: Navreet Josan
Hair:  Baljit Cheema 
Boy (Personal Assisstant): Adith Agarwal
MC Square team :-
MUA: Rajan Passi
Hair: Harry
Choreographer: Jayshree Dinesh dhawan
Assistant stylist: Annie Gulati
VFX Credits: 
VFX:  Inside Motion Pictures
VFX Directors: InsideAKY & Himanshu Dhar
VFX Compositor: Navi Joshi
VFX Artists: Aayous Jain & Krishan Khanna 
Digital Marketing: Underdog Digital
Distribution: Ingrooves Music Group.
Promotions: Underdog Digital
Poster Design: Vicky Sandhu
Travel Partner: PRM Hospitality

Lyrics -

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Nakhro, dekha pahli dafa,
College ke bahar dass kya thi raza,
Chale left to right bata kyu di saza,
Louis, LV tight teri kaidi ada,
Chhore paache paache haande leke landi jeep,
Tere chakkar me kare kaand galt hi cheej,
Gere 5 inch heel, Chhore leve poori feel,
Tere bhaav bhi to fly kare poori dheel,

Makke tip to toe tu poori gach hai,
26 ki kamar poori lachke,
21 ki umar, kya ye sach hai?
Mere bethi hai nishaane pe rah bachke,

Halla mach gaya poore gaam me,
Ib bethak laage shaam ne,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran darja kadi raam te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Tu hoga badmaash tere laake me chhore,
Tere jaise pade fail mere khaate me chhore,
Manne Jhaanse me laane ki koshish na kar,
Maanja padega ghane ghaate me chhore,

Teri chikni chupdi baat me,
Chhori aati koni saath me,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Kyunkar darjua raam te,

Haan me ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani


#GhaniSyaani #MCSquare #ShehnaazGill

snippet.description:
ടൊയോട്ട ഇന്നോവ ക്രിസ്റ്റയുടെ അടുത്ത തലമുറക്കാനായി രംഗത്തെത്തിയിരിക്കുകയാണ് ഇന്നോവ ഹൈക്രോസ്സ്.പെട്രോൾ-ഇലക്ട്രിക്ക് മോട്ടോർ സെറ്റപ്പുള്ള ഹൈക്രോസിന് കമ്പനി പറയുന്ന മൈലേജ് 21 കിലോമീറ്ററാണ്...

ആയിരക്കണക്കിന് പുസ്തകങ്ങൾ ഇനി ദിവസവും 1 രൂപയിൽ താഴെ ചിലവിൽ വർഷം മുഴുവനും കേട്ട് അറിയൂ.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3634 - 6 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3634
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal is trying to get Vidya's phone number, but Bhide keeps turning him down. He switches strategies and hires Goli and Gogi to do the task. Goli and Gogi come to Bhide with a proposal to install an app on his phone and take the number from his phone. However, Bhide notices them instantly and sends Popatlal a stern letter in response. However, Popatlal is obstinate, and along with Goli and Gogi, they use the internet to search for Vidya's school's phone number. They then make the decision to go to Vidya's school and meet her there. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3634, 6 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000198185

snippet.title: Noor Bhai Ki Purani Aashiqui Part 2 || 90's Ki Love Story || Shehbaaz Khan & Team
snippet.description:
Hello Everyone!
We are back with the sequel of “Noor Bhai Ki Purani Ashiqui” 😍❤️. Yes! You heard that right 🤩 the tragedy is not over yet!
I know you guys watched the Part-1 of “Noor Bhai ki Ashiqui” and showed so much love and support, I really appreciate that 🤗❤️.
And on a huge public demand we are back with Part-2 and this video is loaded with lots of Comedy, Drama, love, and suspense….😍
So, What happened next after Noor Bhai’s love “Zubeda” leaves him alone by calling her brother and her son as Mamu. Then after Noor Bhai gets traumatized and depressed thinking about it. The other people also feel sorrow for “Noor Bhai” and one of his friend says “Noor bhai” to just forget her and abuse her for breaking his heart 💔. Noor bhai gets angry and slaps him for abusing her in front of him and tells him how much he loves her.
After time passes… “Noor Bhai” and his friend are busy doing some work then suddenly his Love “Zubeda” approaches….. What did they discuss??? That’s the suspense you should watch the full video to know.
And if you really liked the video, please share it with your family and friends.
Thanks a lot for supporting us always ❤️.

snippet.title: 2022 Toyota Innova Hycross review - India's favourite MPV reborn | First Drive | Autocar India
snippet.description:
The all-new Toyota Innova Hycross is an Innova unlike any before. It makes the radical switch to a monocoque construction and front-wheel drive layout, and it's only on sale with petrol and petrol strong hybrid options. And there's a greater focus on luxury. Gavin D'Souza tells you how it all comes together. 

Cameraperson: Mritunjay Chakarborty
Editor: Mohit Sharma

Kde ghumdi a canada kde uk to streak
Tere insta ne ajkl full farhi peak

3 shota’n di aa maar tera break up kehnde

Satt launda gujji dhill varte na kutt ch ni
Downtown baggiya aa dakkiya rakaane

Mubda soccer player daunda fakkiya rakaane

Fan saale sajjre prahunya de mithiye ni
Hor bhave kamm marhe keete aa bathere
Kde haakr ni maari pind sohnya de mithiye

Utto kiara advani vangu vekhni aa maut
Kde airforce paave kde heal payi hundi
Teri body ne e leerhya ch feel payi hundi

Jatt marriott baithe tinn room aa khlaaye
Kehnde rukna aa raar pattu peshi utte aye
Sade nitt de klesh painda chaddna aa desh 
Kaand vadda ho gya ni khoon jyada cho gya
Te ambulance na pahunchi adde naalde te chaunki
Ohnu ladh laige asi gypsy de vich behge
Bni 26 vatte 26 thode paise poose paige 
Gal mukdi aa banda dabkauna aunda a ni
Sanu gutto’n farh vairi nu mnauna aunda aa 
Sanu dhauno farh vairi nu mnauna aunda aa
Kahlon kahlon

snippet.title: FRENCH FRIES | Crispy French Fried potatoes Recipe Cooking In Village | Finger Chips | Easy Snacks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a French Fried Potato recipe. This French Fries recipe is a simple and easy snack recipe that everyone can cook quickly at home. We first boiled the sliced potatoes, then we sun dried them to make crispy Frech Fries.

Finally, we eat this snack in the evening by adding some hand-ground species masalas. Yummy and Crispy.

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

snippet.description:

Siyani Episode 115 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 7th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib

Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab

Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Brazil 4:1 South Korea - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Brazil stormed into the quarterfinals of the #FIFAWorldCup for a record 17th time after beating South Korea 4-1 at Stadium 974.

The five-time champions stormed to a four-goal lead in the first half through goals from Vinicius Jr, Neymar, Richarlison & Lucas Paqueta.

Tite's side took the foot off the gas in the second half to see out the match. Paik Seung-ho pulled one back for the Asian side with a long-range effort and that was to be the only goal in the final 45 minutes.

Brazil will now face Croatia in the quarter-final on Dec 9, 8:30 pm.

Enjoy the highlights of #BRAKOR & stay tuned to #JioCinema & #Sports18 for more from the #WorldsGreatestShow 📺📲

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 2:1 Australia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the last eight for the 10th time in #FIFAWorldCup history, edging Australia 2-1 at the Ahmad bin Ali Stadium.

Lionel Messi, who hadn't scored in the knockout stages of the competition, opened the scoring in the 35th minute. Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for Lionel Scaloni's side after making the most of an error by Socceroos goalkeeper Mathew Ryan.

Australia pulled one back through an unfortunate own goal by Enzo Fernandez. But Argentina held their nerve to make it through.

Watch Messi & Co. next in action against #Netherlands in the quarter-final on Dec 9 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

snippet.title: Siyani Episode 114 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 6th Dec 2022
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 114 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 6th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib
Saniya Shamshad - Ujala
Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab
Erum Akhter - Reema
Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar
Parveen Akbar - Fazeelat
Beena Chaudhary - Nusrat
Hashim Butt

Ingredients:
Set Dosa
• 1 cup thick Poha
• 1 cup Rava
• 1/2 cup Curd
• 2 1/2 cup Water
• Salt to taste
• 1 tsp Eno fruit salt
• Oil 
Tomato Chutney
• 1 tsp Oil
• 4~5 Garlic cloves
• Curry leaves
• 1 sliced Onion
• 3 Tomatoes
• 3~4 Dry red chilies
• 3~4 Beet slices
• Salt to taste
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1/2 tsp Mustard seeds
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• Pinch of Hing
• Curry leaves
Method: 
Set Dosa
• Blend poha, rava together into powder in mixer and transfer it into a bowl. 
• Add curd, water, salt and mix everything well together. The batter should have pouring 
  consistency. 
• Cover and rest that batter for about 10 minutes. 
• Add Eno fruit salt and mix in quickly.
• You can use 1/4 tsp baking soda in place of Eno. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and brush oil. 
• Add ladleful batter into the pan and spread it a little.
• When lower side is roasted well take it off on wire rack. Set dosa is all ready. 
• You can make 20 set dosa from the proportion we used. 
Tomato Chutney
• Heat up oil in a pan and add garlic, curry leaves, onion, tomatoes, dry red chilies, beet. 
• Fry everything well together for about 7-8 minutes. 
• Turn off the gas and let the mixture cool down.
•  Transfer the mixture into a blender jar and add salt. 
• Blend into puree. Avoid use of water while blending. 
• Heat up oil in a pan and add mustard seeds. 
• When mustard seeds pop up add cumin seeds, hing, curry leaves. 
• Add blended chutney into the pan and mix well. 
• Cook the chutney for about 2-3 minutes.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 115 Teaser - 6th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib

Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab
Erum Akhter - Reema
Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar

Hashim Butt

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3633 - 5 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3633
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide's uncle pays a visit to him who is looking for a suitable spouse for Vidya. Popatlal is listening to their conversation and is pleased that Bhide has been given the task of finding Vidya a suitable spouse. However, Popatlal is surprised when Bhide tells his uncle that he is unaware of any such groom. Excited Popatlal confronts Bhide as the visitors leave his home and requests that he suggest his name for Vidya. Bhide informs him that since their uncle solely wants a teacher for Vidya, his decision is peculiar. Popatlal, who was ecstatic about the wedding, requests that he give him Vidya's contact information because he wants to speak with her and discuss her concerns. Bhide is aggravated by Popatlal's actions and asks him to leave. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3633, 5 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000198072
